query:
SELECT f.id, f.userId, u.name, u.email, f.propertyId, p.address 
FROM favorites f 
JOIN users u ON f.userId = u.id 
JOIN properties p ON f.propertyId = p.id 
WHERE f.propertyId IN (390988, 390719, 390706)
